32)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109332)\">Rom. 9:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106133\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106133)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106133)\">Ex. 9:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114768\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114768)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114768)\">D&amp;C 86:8-10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107650\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107650)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107650)\">Obad. 1:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107286\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107286)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107286)\">Isa. 61:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107001\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107001)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107001)\">Isa. 1:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109338\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109338)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109338)\">Rom. 9:29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114773\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114773)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114773)\">D&amp;C 86:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115702\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115702)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115702)\">D&amp;C 113:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <sp